data.description: ***If you are looking for your NEW HOME, I have a Move-In Ready Abode seeking a New Owner!!! This 3 Bedroom, 1 Bathroom property situated on almost a quarter acre lot, so make arrangements for your showing today. The property has beautiful hardwood floors, granite countertops throughout the kitchen and bathroom, a screened porch which offers an extra living space for entertaining or quiet away time. Your NEW home has a two year old roof, an extended driveway, a utility room with washer/dryer hook-ups, a spacious open front yard, and a fenced-in back yard allowing abundant growth opportunities.***  >>>Make your showing reservation "today" for your New HOME!!!<<<
